# world/ environment — documents the contract. Copy to .env.local and fill in.

# Required for the NPC conversation brain (api/chat.js). Server-side only —
# this key must NEVER reach the browser. Locally it's read by `vercel dev`;
# in production set it in the Vercel project's environment variables.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the chat model (defaults to claude-haiku-4-5 for latency).
# CHAT_MODEL=
